Introduce data specification module.

This introduces a protolite-based data specification module that can be
imported in other modules (both Java and Kotlin supported). This
approach is based on various resources including
https://medium.com/@elye.project/android-protobuf-in-kotlin-a1c33014a4e2,
https://proandroiddev.com/how-to-setup-your-android-app-to-use-protobuf-96132340de5c,
https://github.com/google/protobuf-gradle-plugin, and others.
